file.name: test_order_spec.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Test spec for OpenAPI3RouterFactoryTest.mountHandlersOrderTest()
paths:
  /product/special:
    get:
      summary: Get special product
      operationId: showSpecialProduct
      responses:
        default:
          description: ok
  /product/{id}:
    get:
      summary: Product detail
      operationId: showProductById
      parameters:
        - name: id
          in: path
          required: true
          description: The id of the product to retrieve
          schema:
            type: integer
            format: int32
      responses:
        default:
          description: ok
